title: MASH OST (1970) Johnny Mandel - Robert Altman
description:
MASH (1970) Robert Altman

Music by Johnny Mandel

rendition of the M.A.S.H. theme by Ahmad Jamal
 
01 - M.A.S.H. Theme (Ahmad Jamal) (2:48)
02 - Duke and Hawkeye Arrive at M.A.S.H. (10:43)
03 - The Operating Theater (1:06)
04 - Major Houlihan and Major Burns (6:43)

05 - Painless Suicide, Funeral and Resurrection (8:02)

vinyl rip, MP3 Audio: 256 Kbps, 44,100 Hz, 16 Bit, Stereo.

Album cover: 

MASH_front_cover.jpg
MASH_back_cover.jpg


Attention, attention: this OST is for the feature FILM, not the 
ridiculous teevee show... (...seriously, there is NO comparison.) 

Like the Monty Python records, this one has lots and lots of dialog
mixed in with a few musical tracks. Over and out.

In memoriam: Robert Altman 1934-2006
